                  <provenance>Walda ʾƎgziʾ, Walatta Madḫǝn and Tawalda
                     Madḫǝn are mentioned in the concluding supplication on <locus target="#67v">67v</locus>. They are also mentioned in the supplication formulas: Walatta
                     Madḫǝn (<locus target="#4rb">4rb</locus>, 46va 53ra, 58ra), Tawalda Madḫǝn
                     (<locus target="#53ra">53ra</locus>), Walda Śǝllāse (<locus target="#33ra">33ra</locus>), Gabra Madḫǝn (<locus target="#46va">46va</locus>), Ḫāyla
                     Śǝllāse (<locus from="57vb" to="58ra">57vb-58ra</locus>).</provenance>
